      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/136/15",
      "text": [
        " «يَأْكُلُ مِنْ أُضْحِيَّتِهِ وَ يَتَصَدَّقُ بِالْفِدَاءِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3057 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) was asked about the atonement for hunting: can the individual eat from its meat?\nImam (as) replied: \"He eats from his sacrificial offering and gives the atonement in charity.\""
        ]
      }
